abraflexi-api-doc (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add a JSON column alongside every XML API-payload example, laid out
    side by side in a two-column table, so both wire formats can be
    compared at a glance
  * Add appendix: reference list of all AbraFlexi evidence codes with
    descriptive names, sourced from php-spojenet-abraflexi's
    EvidenceList.json
  * Add appendix: default agenda access rights per user role, sourced
    from Flexplorer's permissions.csv
  * Add an "Edit this page" link to every page (rendered by the shibuya
    theme used for the packaged docs), pointing at the page's source file
    on GitHub
  * Show the documentation version in the page footer
  * Link the php-abraflexi and python-abraflexi client library projects
    from the README

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 11:30:00 +0200

